    "text": "2,000+ mathematicians just signed one document about AI.\n\nTerence Tao endorsed it. Peter Scholze endorsed it. The International Mathematical Union endorsed it.\n\nThe outlets covering it are framing it as \"AI is overhyped.\"\n\nThey missed the real point. It's the strongest case ever https://t.co/BzbHIAwBQh",
