    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "This is the Leiden Declaration on AI and Mathematics.\n\nHere's the line the headlines skipped. Today's AI can produce arguments that look correct, read correct, and are nearly impossible to tell apart from a real proof. And are wrong.\n\nSo they drew a line. Use the tools, but the",
