    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "None of this threatens what I do. It's the opposite.\n\nThe model is the execution layer. Your thinking is the engine.\n\nThis declaration quietly splits the room in two. People who paste a prompt and trust the output, and people who run a thinking system and verify before they",
