    "is_retweet": false
  },
  {
    "username": "godofprompt",
    "nickname": "God of Prompt",
    "text": "The most credentialed humans on earth just published the operating principle for this entire era.\n\nLLMs don't think; you do.\n\nThe people who internalize that build an unfair advantage.\n\nThe people who wait for the model to think for them get left holding plausible, confident,",
